    "title": "Tudagu.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Tudagu has an armoured light grey body with bony wings and the head of a frog. It dribbles constantly.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 146     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: +++      </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ +    </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: x..     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: +..      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: High    </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\n\n\nYou have about 56% to hit with the +5 lajatang \"Rive\" and 38% to hit with your slice and slice.\nIt has about 5% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  After Damaging Hits\nHit     49          Cause weakness     \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.",
